, or a reference item."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If the typographical item does not already have"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a font set, this will set the font to “system font”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"using the provided size."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Size can be expressed as a percentage of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"“container” height (e.g. 30%) with the percentage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"relative to height of font – "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"cap height"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For example, a value of 100% will cause the visual"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"height of the font (or cap height) to be approximately"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"100% of the size of the container."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(Alternatively, provide a relative axis of “horizontal”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to get a percentage of the container width, or “both”"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"axes to get a percentage of the average between the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"container height and width.)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"For convenience, if the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"item"}]},{"type":"text","text":" does not have size for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the specified axis, the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"parent or parent guide"}]},{"type":"text","text":" size"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for that axis will be used. Alternatively, specify a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"query reference for percentage-based values to be"},{"type":"text","text"